      <h2>Only Pay for What You Use</h2>
      <p>
        With an in house team or traditional agency, you bear the cost of full time employees and management overhead. With Banzai, you only pay for what you use.
      </p>
      <a class="btn btn-default" href="/features" role="button">View Features</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row front-page-mid-section">
    <div class="col-md-2 icon hidden-sm hidden-xs">
      <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-signal" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <h2>Outbound Sales in the Cloud</h2>
      <p>
        Save weeks of meetings, planning, and management. Launching a Banzai campaign is as simple and fast as launching an email marketing campaign.
      </p>
      <a class="btn btn-default" href="/features" role="button">View Features</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row front-page-mid-section">
    <div class="col-md-2 icon hidden-sm hidden-xs">
      <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-dashboard" aria-hidden="true"></span>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-8">
      <h2>Campaign Reporting</h2>
      <p>
        Performance metrics matter. Banzai includes detailed reporting for leads, call outcomes, and other campaign data, and integrates with the CRM and marketing systems you already use.
      </p>
      <a class="btn btn-default" href="/features" role="button">View Features</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
